{"tid":1330578,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"野餐飲食指南","createTime":"2019-07-18T15:28:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T16:21:21.000Z","uid":50144,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"8d122c3f79be079e007e09c433208fba0708a9e2","tid":1330578,"uid":50144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T15:28:33.000Z","msg":"乾糧有好多種，不過野餐興高采烈時見到梳打餅其實唔太開胃，Mars嗰類朱古力會溶，麥記包擺多陣又會臭，又冇理由要餓成日。<br />\n<br />\n如果每個人發夢野餐時自備energy bar同蛋糕仔等食物補充體力，一嚟可以減少物資需要，同埋確保前線keep住有能量補充。<br />\n<br />\n選擇方面，嘉頓瑞士卷之類獨立包裝方便，有錢啲嘅可以準備能量啫哩同bar，豐儉由人，不過食得多energy products記得飲返多少少水。<br />\n<br />\n如果鍾意自己整嘢食嘅，食譜YouTube大把，點樣pack可以參考下面段片。<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/OHhT3rDNTpM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FOHhT3rDNTpM&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHEwVsaiM9baN%2FEtUhsAXiQ7E%3D&h=b8fce9dd\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/OHhT3rDNTpM</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n21號萬事小心，有啲老母鍾意亂放狗。"},{"pid":"73a3deae7ab242bd9c6ee80df2c4994d6f68f22a","tid":1330578,"uid":50144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T16:21:21.000Z","msg":"721見"}]}